admin_disabled_screen_description.message:
Your G Suite administrator has turned on Google Chat. Collaborate in team rooms and share files easily with Chat.

For the best experience, make sure to uninstall this extension after installing the new Google Chat app.

chrome_app_description.message: Hangouts Chrome App is deprecated. Please switch to the Hangouts Chrome Extension.

chrome_ext_description.message: Hangouts brings conversations to life with photos, emoji, and even group video calls for free.
